title: Pete and Pete - 309 - Road Warrior.avi
description:
Pete & Pete is set in the fictional town of Wellsville; like The Simpsons&#039; Springfield, its state is never revealed, even though there is a Wellsville, New York in Allegany County, and another, much smaller, in Montgomery County, as well as others in Colorado, Connecticut, Kansas, Michigan, Missouri, Ohio, Pennsylvania, Tennessee, and Utah. In addition, Glurt County, mentioned in "Yellow Fever" and "The Good, the Bad and the Lucky," does not exist.

The Adventures of Pete and Pete. Season 3 Episode 9 (309)30 November 1995. 

Big Pete and his friends reach the age of responsibility and take Driver&#039;s Ed from Mr. Slurm, the shop teacher.

This is my first upload, saw that this episode was missing from another torrent. I got it from someone else so don&#039;t blame me if you don&#039;t like the quality. Otherwise enjoy.

Long-time listener, first-time caller. Hope to provide more enjoyment and entertainment in the future
